# Field Guide Style Guide

## Find/Replace Rules
1) `^\s*#{1,6}\s*FG[- ]?(\d{1,4})\s*[â€”-]\s*(.+)$` â†’ `### FG-\1 â€” \2`
2) `FG-(\d{1,2})(?=\s)` â†’ `FG-00\1`
3) `FG-(\d{3})(?=\s)` â†’ `FG-0\1`
4) `(âš–ï¸ \*\*Core Message:\*\* [^\n]+)(?:\n(?!- ğŸ“–|\Z).*)*` â†’  
   `$1
   - ğŸ“– **Lesson Content:** 
   - âœï¸ **Assignment:** 
   - âœ… **Model Response:** 
   - ğŸ’¡ **Reflection Summary:** 
   - ğŸ¨ **Visual Concept:** Illustrative: . | Conceptual: .`
5) `^### FG-(\d{3,4}) â€” (.+)$` â†’ append `\n<!-- id: fg-\1 -->`

